Author: calem
Title: [ANN][ICO] FolleX™ - Social Exchange Token [SET]
Body: That is my role within the ICO. There shall be many.  It's all still in the works but I'm always open to suggestions if anyone comes forward with something neat, novel and presentable/functionable. Anything that gets the word or tokens efficiently out there, will be considered.  But please, no spamming with stuff like offers for running a banner in your signature or lame stuff like that which ANYONE can do. I'm not running that sort of bounty program. I really need people to bring quality stuff to the table. You wont just be collecting a bounty. You will be building a rapport with the founders and team for future projects. Meaning, I'll keep you in mind for the next project when or if it comes along.
